# Cloudflare Pages routing for moavoca.com
#
# Static assets (HTML pages, _expo bundle, etc.) are served from disk
# first by CF Pages — only paths with no matching file fall through to
# these rules. We only need a SPA fallback for the Expo Web subpath so
# Expo Router-driven dynamic routes (e.g. /app/wordlist/<uuid>,
# /app/invite/<code>) hand control to the client bundle. Static landing
# at / and the legal docs at /privacy.html etc. are unaffected because
# they exist on disk and resolve before this rule.

/app/*    /app/index.html    200
